{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/people/nick-goodwin","content_id":"693e9499-fc1c-44e2-9b3e-68af6a78253f","description":"Nick Goodwin was appointed Chief Executive of HM Courts and Tribunals Service (HMCTS) in March 2022. Before joining HMCTS, he was Chief Executive and Public Guardian in the Office of the Public Guardian (OPG) from July 2019. Before that, Nick was director for access to justice policy at the Ministry of Justice .","details":{"body":"<p>Nick Goodwin was appointed Chief Executive of <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-courts-and-tribunals-service\">HM Courts and Tribunals Service (HMCTS)</a> in March 2022.</p>\n\n<p>Before joining HMCTS, he was Chief Executive and Public Guardian in the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-of-the-public-guardian\">Office of the Public Guardian (OPG)</a> from July 2019. Before that, Nick was director for access to justice policy at the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice\">Ministry of Justice</a>.</p>\n","full_name":"Nick Goodwin","image":{"alt_text":"Nick Goodwin","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/64ae70a58bc29f000d2ccb2c/s465_Nick-Goodwin-HMCTS-CEO.jpg"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","first_published_at":"2019-07-19T14:23:57+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/nick-goodwin.cy","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/nick-goodwin.cy","base_path":"/government/people/nick-goodwin.cy","content_id":"693e9499-fc1c-44e2-9b3e-68af6a78253f","document_type":"person","links":{},"locale":"cy","public_updated_at":"2023-07-12T09:21:41Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Nick Goodwin","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/nick-goodwin.cy","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/nick-goodwin","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/nick-goodwin","base_path":"/government/